subject: Baseball
lead_paragraph: No October baseball for Derek Jeter, but he did have a victory to talk about. Jeter and Tiger Woods were working on a promotion for Gillette, and Jeter said he took Woods down in “FaceBreaker” video boxing. “We were just playing a game which I beat him in a few times,” Jeter said. “We’ve got video, photos, all the proof.”.
